OL,3,CConstance Marten 'given almost #50k by
OL,4,Ctrust fund in months before search'
OL,6,FA fugitive aristocrat was given almost
OL,7,F#50,000 from her trust fund in the
OL,8,Fmonths before she disappeared with her
OL,9,Fpartner and newborn baby, a court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FConstance Marten was given #47,886 by
OL,13,FC. Hoare & Co between September 1 2022
OL,14,Fand January 17 2023.
OL,16,FA police appeal to find them was
OL,17,Flaunched on 6 January last year.
