OL,3,CConstance Marten 'given almost #50k by
OL,4,Ctrust fund in months before search'
OL,6,FMarten, 36, and Mark Gordon, 49, went
OL,7,Fon the run with their daughter
OL,8,FVictoria after their car burst into
OL,9,Fflames near Bolton, Greater
OL,10,FManchester, last January.
OL,12,FThe Old Bailey has heard how they went
OL,13,Fon to sleep in a tent, in a bid to
OL,14,Fkeep the baby, after Marten's four
OL,15,Fother children were taken into care.
OL,17,FWhen the couple were eventually
OL,18,Farrested in Brighton, East Sussex,
OL,19,Fthey initially refused to say where
OL,20,Ftheir child was or whether she was
OL,21,Falive or dead.
