OL,3,CConstance Marten 'given almost #50k by
OL,4,Ctrust fund in months before search'
OL,6,FThe jury heard during evidence from
OL,7,Fpolice financial investigator
OL,8,FDetective Constable Steve Ferguson on
OL,9,FThursday that Marten is the
OL,10,Fbeneficiary of a family trust, and she
OL,11,Fwas given a monthly stipend, but ad
OL,12,Fhoc payments could also be given if
OL,13,FMarten asked for them.
OL,15,FA monthly allowance of #2,500 was
OL,16,Finitially given in September 2022, and
OL,17,Fsome of the money could be given early
OL,18,Fthen deducted from the next payment if
OL,19,FMarten requested it, the court heard.
