OL,3,CConstance Marten 'given almost #50k by
OL,4,Ctrust fund in months before search'
OL,6,FA sum of #1,200 was transferred in
OL,7,FNovember for the storage of Marten's
OL,8,Fbelongings, there were a number of
OL,9,Femails about the purchase of a car in
OL,10,FDecember, before #15,590 was
OL,11,Ftransferred and #13,596 was sent for
OL,12,Fcamera/filming equipment and a laptop.
OL,14,FThe allowance then rose to #3,400 a
OL,15,Fmonth, before C. Hoare & Co began to
OL,16,Fsend emails trying to contact Marten
OL,17,Fat about the same time the police
OL,18,Fappeal was launched.
