OL,3,CConstance Marten 'given almost #50k by
OL,4,Ctrust fund in months before search'
OL,6,FOn 6 January 2023, the bank sent
OL,7,FMarten an email asking her to call,
OL,8,Fthree days later they emailed again
OL,9,Fsaying they were "concerned for her
OL,10,Fwelfare", then on 12 January they
OL,11,Fagain contacted her to say they were
OL,12,F"very concerned" and asked her to
OL,13,Furgently contact them.
OL,15,FJoel Smith, prosecuting, said the
OL,16,Ftotal amount transferred during that
OL,17,Ftime was #47,886.
