OL,3,CConstance Marten 'given almost #50k by
OL,4,Ctrust fund in months before search'
OL,6,FAfter 5 January, the date the couple's
OL,7,Fcar was found burning, there were "no
OL,8,Fsignificant card payments made", the
OL,9,Fcourt heard.
OL,11,FIn early January 2023, Marten's Metro
OL,12,FBank balance was #19,083.18.
OL,14,FMarten and Gordon, of no fixed
OL,15,Faddress, deny manslaughter, perverting
OL,16,Fthe course of justice, concealing the
OL,17,Fbirth of a child, child cruelty and
OL,18,Fcausing or allowing the death of a
OL,19,Fchild.
OL,21,FThe Old Bailey trial continues.
